It's a DFS game that is playable by anybody on any day – covering NFL now and MLB, NHL and NBA coming soon. It's open and accessible to the causal sports fans and griders alike. If the side chosen wins, winnings are received instantly. Best of all, Syde is fully legal, (check out their FAQ), and allows users to invite and challenge friends via social feeds.
